# Browser Screenshot Path

When calling `browser_take_screenshot`, always specify the `filename` parameter with a path inside `/Users/esoh/Documents/Labs/VPK-rovodev/output/`. Choose a descriptive filename and subfolder structure that fits the context.

**Never** omit the `filename` parameter — the default saves `page-{timestamp}.png` into the current working directory, scattering files across the workspace root.

Examples:
- `/Users/esoh/Documents/Labs/VPK-rovodev/output/plan-light.png`
- `/Users/esoh/Documents/Labs/VPK-rovodev/output/dark-mode-check.png`
- `/Users/esoh/Documents/Labs/VPK-rovodev/output/screenshot-2026-02-19T12-00-00.png`
